			<_body type="a">{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1250\deff0\deflang1045{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset238{\*\fname Arial;}Arial CE;}}%0D
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\f0\fs20 State indication\par%0D
Optionally, the lamp will be blinking, possibly with different rate in case of opening and closing the gate\par%0D
